Comment: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:13.50,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Trip to the world.
Comment: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:15.40,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Here we go to an unknown world.
Comment: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:17.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a newborn traveler.
Comment: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.20,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Unstable footsteps are fun to watch.
Comment: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.30,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Get things done right, only when needed.
Comment: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:22.82,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people in this world...
Comment: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:25.12,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...sometimes, you'll receive slanders.
Comment: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:27.16,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's warp uninteresting things...
Comment: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:28.65,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...and lead at least a rational life.
