Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:26.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani had an accident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:27.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night he hit the guardrail\Ndriving the downhill on Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:34.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His injury isn't too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:36.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just minor whiplash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:39.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's really torn up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His car was heavily damaged, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:46.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the race on Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:49.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:52.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we have to find a substitute\Nfor Iketani somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Iketani...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright to be walking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In the back garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:06.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's been done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't start until we get all the parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want fried tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You had an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:56.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much time till the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:04.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to ask you a favor\Nabout that, Mr. Fujiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:05.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:06.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:10.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you drive in the race instead\Nof me the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, Mr. Fujiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:19.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:24.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand how\Na Road Racer feels, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The local drivers can't be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:33.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, even if I do, I'd just be an\Nold man in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:36.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I... grew up driving Akina...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:41.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I can tell that those Redsuns guys are looking\Ndown on all of Akina's Road Racers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:42.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{SOREDE}That's why I'm so frustrated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:48.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{AKINA}I want to show them there's a skilled\NRoad Racer on Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:51.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fujiwara, you can\Ndo that because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:55.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've defeated Takahashi,\Nthe fastest of Akagi, once already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Mr. Fujiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:10.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NWe're closed for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so rigid.\NFill it up with high octane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How cheeky...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,High octane for the Eight-Six,\Nyou said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:26.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who told Iketani\Nthat ridiculous rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:30.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I didn't mean to tell a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:36.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He came over today with bandages\Nand neck brace on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:39.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to drive instead of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hate that kind of guy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:45.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, then why not drive instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani's a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:53.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an adult poking\Nhis nose in a kids' fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:59.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you send\Na kid to a kids' fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really good, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:12.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if it's Akina's downhill, he's good\Nenough not to lose to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he can't defeat me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes your fighting instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:20.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what made him so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:24.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he's asked, he's not the kind\Nwho'll accept so easily and drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:30.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll come up with a plan for the\Nsake of the bandaged Iketani.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Don't break your promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:54.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I hate people who smoke\Nand break promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:58.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me use the car on Sunday, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunday...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:00.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do the delivery in the\Nmorning as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:10.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a meeting of the Society of Commerce\Non Sunday, so I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:16.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I really need the car this Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so stubborn,\Nand let me use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the car isn't\Nthat great for your use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go without asking, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:32.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The car won't run\Nwithout a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it on a string and\Nwear it around my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:36.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:40.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so desperate,\NI can consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:51.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Saturday night, beat the pants off a smartass\Nkid who claims to be the fastest on Akagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...on Akina's downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,H...how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:58.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll let you use the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:01.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you get a full tank of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Full tank of gas...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Full tank of gas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:11.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That's so irresistible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...'cause I'm almost broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,L...let me think about\Nit for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:23.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, think as much as you want.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0130,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Takahashi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Keisuke, good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:50.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:54.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the Eight-Six\Nyou saw on Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:57.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you logically explain\Nwhy it was so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:03.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at that kind\Nof thing like you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:08.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I always say, the most important\Nthing in driving technique is "this."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:13.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can figure out anything\Nby driving behind your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:18.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,From the opponent's habits and weaknesses,\Nto how well the suspension is set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:22.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Your analysis skill is\Nalmost monstrous{incredible}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:30.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, you're incredible because you\Ncan keep up with me without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:34.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can apply theories to\Nyour driving skill, it's ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:38.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was defeated the other day because\Nof unfamiliarity and carelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had such\Na disgrace before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:44.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The inside of that Eight-Six\Nmust be monstrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:46.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Monstrous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:54.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should watch\Nthe race tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Saturday has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "So what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The race!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The race against the Akagi Redsuns!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:20.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me you'd borrow the Eight-Six\Nand we'd go see it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:24.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:26.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:32.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even say that you can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:36.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:40.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cancel, I won't be seeing you anymore,\Nno matter what the reason is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:45.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've kept counting the\Ndays to go until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:46.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:48.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:50.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want fried tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:11:00.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fujiwara, please come\Nto the race today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:11.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, I might be able to go to\Ntonight's race on Mt. Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:24.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it's definite...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:28.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the chance is fifty-fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's gonna start?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:32.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The friendship rally\Nbegins at 9:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the time attack\Nbegins at 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten o'clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:41.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Eight-Six doesn't appear\Nby ten, give up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll have to do\Nsomething yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:46.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting, Mr. Fujiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you'll definitely come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.\NI said fifty percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:55.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've already decided to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you, along with\Nall the team members.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:03.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Mr. Fujiwara, I'll be waiting\Nat Akina's peak at 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:20.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can't help myself when it comes\Nto an eager guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:23.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If Takumi refuses,\Nshould I drive myself...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Boy, I'm getting excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:53.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Something good happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting a little different than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You look happy for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:06.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm going to the beach\Nwith my friend tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking\Nforward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend, you mean a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:15.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No!  It's a girl of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:20.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what it is, I can buy you a new\Nbathing suit at the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:25.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought myself one already.\NI don't need two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:28.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you in the bathing suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:31.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll be sunny tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:40.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask such a dumb question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be sunny all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:44.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:50.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,SAY WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:54.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so envious!\NI wanna go to the beach, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:55.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:59.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...YOU'RE GOING WITH A GIRL!\NIS A GITL GOING WITH YOU?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:03.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,WHO IS IT?!\NDo I know her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:05.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she cute?!\NDoes she have big boobs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:12.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi Natsuki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:16.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cruel, going ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:20.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but the situation didn't\Ngive me a chance to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Some other time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen during the race today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:36.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the Redsuns have won\Nevery race they've challenged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The outcome is so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Akina team will be totally nailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:43.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fastest in Gunma aren't the Redsuns...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:46.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but us, the Night Kids of Myogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi, it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:49.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:15:00.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The R32 is a pure thoroughbred,\Nborn to run fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:03.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It'll never be defeated by the\Nrotary potatoes of Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}There's gonna be a little\Nparty on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The story about the race\Nbetween Iketani's team...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:24.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...and the fastest team on Akagi,\Nhas been talked about everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I wonder which side's gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:34.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Well, Takumi's Eight-Six\Nis Bunta's car as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...so it won't be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:40.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm getting excited\Nafter such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:52.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There're so many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:55.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such big\Ngalleries on Akina before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:16:00.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Redsuns drew them here\Nto show off their speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be so disgraceful if we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, about the Eight-Six\Nyou talked about earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:08.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really true, Iketani?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:09.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:14.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hard for me to believe\Nin that Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:18.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Takahashi's FD3S is moderately\Ntuned for the mountain path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:22.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they say it produces at least 350 HP.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got so much power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:29.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's downhill, the Eight-Six\Nwill be no match for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:32.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani, did you get hit\Nsomewhere really bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:36.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's the Eight-Six,\Nit's not a normal Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:41.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi Keisuke himself said that it\Nlooked like a normal panda Trueno...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:44.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's a monster machine\Nunder the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:48.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.  He'll come for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The galleries are so big...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:17:00.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I don't want them to say\Nthe Speedstars ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:04.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:09.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji, for the sake of the team,\Nyou drive like hell to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Y...you must be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:18.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Many cars are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the rotary sound also!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Redsuns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:33.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!\NThe Redsuns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}They've finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:57.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takahashi brothers are incredibly popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:18:01.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the sons of a doctor who\Nruns a big clinic in Takasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't compete with the rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:10.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Driving skill depends on how much\Ngas and tires are wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is Takumi doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The race is gonna begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I made sure,\Nthat stupid Takumi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:28.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, jerk!\NYou're not my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:35.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to make it in time.\NI'd better go on my scooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:39.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the time attack\Nat 10:00 as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:44.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's late, there'll be no other\Ntraffic, making it easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:48.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use radios at the start\Nand finish to time them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:54.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put officials at the blind corners, so\Nthe drivers can go as fast as they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:59.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's oncoming traffic, we'll use\Nlights to signal the drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem so experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:06.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess they do time\Nattacks in many places.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:11.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, it's gonna be a free run\Ntill 10:00, so let's have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:13.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The galleries are packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:30.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:35.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they going to hide their secret\Nweapon until the last moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:39.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It's the bottom of the ninth, one out,\Nwith the bases loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:42.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NHave you decided to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:45.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like it though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? Don't you have\Nthe confidence to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drive like you always do,\Nyou won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:03.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!\NIt's Keisuke's FD3S!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:17.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!\NThe entry speed was so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:21.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Takahashi Ryosuke this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!  Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:41.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Takahashi Ryosuke.\NHis skill is the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! They don't\Nhit at that distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the famous parallel drift!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:02.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a difficult one to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:08.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be done without the skill to control\Nyour speed and line during a drift.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:12.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only a performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:15.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They drive differently when they race.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The ghost of Akina hasn't arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:36.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}You're my only opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Come out, Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:54.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you giving me a paper cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:58.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need one, because\Nyou're not carrying tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:02.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for a delivery, so have fun.
