Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.09,0:24:31.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.40,0:24:33.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, ghost of Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.91,0:24:36.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're scared\Nand ran away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.55,0:24:38.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Do you think you can win this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.99,0:24:41.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!  There's no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.17,0:24:44.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get revenge no matter what!
